This paper is primarily focused on security and authentication on mobile devices, which falls under the category of "Computer Science and Cryptography" (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the user experience and usability of the proposed authentication system, which could also fall under "Human-Computer Interaction" (cs.HC). The paper also mentions the importance of protecting personal data on mobile devices, which could fall under "Computer and Society" (cs.CY). The proposed system involves collecting and analyzing touch behavior data, which could fall under "Signal Processing" (cs.SI) or "Multimedia" (cs.MM).
